Package io.codeleaf.config

Provides the classes to load a configuration.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Configuration
    Represents a Configuration.
    ConfigurationProvider
    This class is used to obtain configurations.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigurationProvider.Holder
    Holder for a singleton, to obtain the singleton, use ConfigurationProvider.get()
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    ConfigurationException
    Thrown when any exception related to the Configuration library occurred.
    ConfigurationNotFoundException
    Thrown when no ConfigurationFactory is present that can create the specified type.
